## ⚠ WARNING – Defensive Training Material ⚠

The email samples contained in this directory are based on real-world phishing campaigns and have been modified for educational and defensive security training purposes.

The following conditions apply:

1. Archive passwords are provided only within the official print and PDF versions of the published material.
2. All URLs, domains, and email addresses have been defanged (e.g., "[.]" substitutions).
3. These materials are provided strictly for defensive education and incident response training. Use for offensive, malicious, or unauthorized purposes is prohibited.

Note:
Anti-virus software may generate alerts when interacting with these files.

Before analyzing any samples:

1. Do NOT execute, open, or interact with these files on production systems or networks.
2. All analysis must be performed within isolated laboratory environments (e.g., offline virtual machines or sandbox environments).